0.6.0
=====

- Major speed improvements [Jorn Baayen]
- Support album cover drag & drop in the "Play album" window [Lee Willis]
- New about logo [Andreas Kwiatkowski]
- Sort songs by title, then by artist [Jorn Baayen]
- Sort albums by artist, then year, then title [Teemu Tervo]
- Various other fixes [Kenneth Christiansen, Jorn Baayen]

Updated translations:
- Brazilian Portuguese [Afonso Celso Medina]
